              <h2><i><b>The Monk FAQ</b></i></h2>
<p>Frequently asked questions on the Monkly-Business Boards.

<h3>Contents</h3>

<p>This FAQ originated as a EZBoard thread that started because the monkly-business boards were becoming very cluttered with the same questions, over and over again.

<p>The most recent version of this FAQ can be found as a stickied post in the <a href="http://pub38.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm2.showMessage?topicID=959.topic">Guides and Tactics</a> forum, and updates added there will be incorporated here. 

<p>The FAQ is spread across 2 articles, and the second part, containing Guides and Tactics, Skills and Stats, information about these boards, and misc info can be found <a  href="http://www.monkly-business.com/articles2.asp?ArticleNum=164"> >>here<< </a>

